executionFailure.embedTitle: Ocorreu um erro inesperadamente inesperado, gomenasai!
executionFailure.fieldValue:
As we probably don't know about this error, you can either [open an issue](https://github.com/RabbitHouseCorp/ChinoKafuu/issues/new/choose) on GitHub or contact us in our [support server](https://discord.gg/rabbithouse). Don't forget to attach this _little message_ when reporting the error.
Thanks and sorry!
